column5: You NASCAR guys know how the race went tonight. Just a week ago I met tonights race winner and last years champion Brad Keselowski. Just a lousy phone pic, but here it is.
If that's Keselowski's beer I hope it was after he drove. How much did he pay you for your autograph?
No.. that's definitely Dan's beer ! One weeekend together and you know me that well, eh?
Penski should have stuck with Dodge, where they were the sole funded team. IMO, glad to see BK with a win though, it must be frustrating after last years golden run.
All these trips down South and you keep forgetting to stop over in Virginia.  Art
